ads.custom_css: @-webkit-keyframes made-visible{0%{pointer-events:none}80%{pointer-events:none}100%{pointer-events:initial}}@keyframes made-visible{0%{pointer-events:none}80%{pointer-events:none}100%{pointer-events:initial}}@-webkit-keyframes made-blurred{0%{-webkit-filter:blur(5px);filter:blur(5px)}80%{-webkit-filter:blur(5px);filter:blur(5px)}100%{-webkit-filter:unset;filter:unset}}@keyframes made-blurred{0%{-webkit-filter:blur(5px);filter:blur(5px)}80%{-webkit-filter:blur(5px);filter:blur(5px)}100%{-webkit-filter:unset;filter:unset}}#_flexbar_ .flexbar-center{-webkit-animation:made-visible 0.5s ease-in-out normal 1.3s forwards,made-blurred 0.5s ease-in-out normal 1s forwards;animation:made-visible 0.5s ease-in-out normal 1.3s forwards,made-blurred 0.5s ease-in-out normal 1s forwards;-webkit-filter:blur(5px);filter:blur(5px);pointer-events:none}
